6.1 Global Conventions

Convention

Value

Base URL

https://api.foundry-iam.com

Version prefix

/v1

Content-Type

application/json

Authentication

Authorization: Bearer <portal_jwt> or Authorization: ApiKey <key>

Idempotency

Idempotency-Key header on all mutating requests

IDs

ULID prefixed: tnt_, wsp_, app_, inv_

Timestamps

ISO 8601 with timezone (TIMESTAMPTZ)

Pagination

cursor-based: ?cursor=<id>&limit=<n> (all list endpoints)

Errors

{ "error": { "code": "", "message": "", "details": {}, "request_id": "" } }

Rate limiting

200 req/min per IP (Redis). 429 returns Retry-After header.



